    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >H+H=H2是一个包含伪化学的类推箱游戏 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220520/extras/9e0c47e1fc734042ca2fe550f156c976.avif?t=1748579489\" width=300 height=80 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 可爱的像素风格 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 以化学为基础的伪化学机制 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 60个手工制造的关卡 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 单人纸牌小游戏 </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220520/extras/340ca2cfcfab067ad2b7c7e50b81566f.avif?t=1748579489\" width=300 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >基础机制要求你碰撞每一个氢原子使得整个关卡没有氢原子存在 </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >H + H = H2 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >H + H2 = H3 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >H3不能被推动 </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220520/extras/90e62ab14b1e827bc71b2f482c3d0c73.poster.avif?t=1748579489\" width=304 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220520/extras/90e62ab14b1e827bc71b2f482c3d0c73.webm?t=1748579489\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220520/extras/90e62ab14b1e827bc71b2f482c3d0c73.mp4?t=1748579489\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当你在游戏中取得进展，会出现更多的机制：比如He原子可以推动任何东西包括H3(?)原子，等等 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220520/extras/0673d8d23fdcfdde4fc855044e058c64.avif?t=1748579489\" width=300 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个独特的单人纸牌受Zachtronics的Fortune’s Foundation启发</p>",
